Dialogs.Dialog: I Can't help it, I'll feed you.
Do you want Rinko to feed you？
Wait, don't we look like an idiot couple？
I actually admire this kind of thing.
Make it the one Rinko likes.
Which one you choose is important.
Will you feed it to Rinko？
Don't spill it before you eat it.
I can't believe you fed me... hehe.
Will you feed me？ ...I get it.
Hehe, I might be a little happy.
You look like a little bird... interesting.
Okay... can you open your mouth？
It takes skill to feed you.
Don't keep me waiting, I'm pretty embarrassed.
It's a big service for you.
Do you have a habit of chewing only with one side？
Don't look at me when you eat.
Oh... there's something on your mouth.
Ah. You have a stain on your mouth.
Ah！ You're leaving that on your mouth in purpose？
Rinko could have taken it for you.
Hehe, do you want me to feed you？
I can't believe I let you feed me...
What are you going to feed me？
I'd like to eat something tasty.
Hey, I want some of that.
You know... I want to eat.
Hey, you know what I mean？
Umm... I wish you'd let me eat.
You're looking at me with curious eyes...
Don't look at me too much.
I'm probably most nervous when I'm waiting.
I don't know what I'm doing.
Make sure you feed me properly...
Can do it, can do it.
Well, that was fun, wasn't it？
Don't you still want to continue？
We can feed each other again with this, okay？
I might remember it later and smile.
You and Rinko are a lovey- dovey couple, no matter how you look at it.
Hah... these are the moments of happiness.
I like this kind of thing.
It's like a couple's event... might be nice♪
Hey, why don't you try this？
I'll blow on the food... Here you go.
Oh, do you want some too？ Here you go, ▲小早川＊▲.
